Package: LinearJ
Type: Package
Title: Higher-order summary statistics for point patterns on linear networks
Version: 0.1.5
Author: person("Mehdi", "Moradi", email = "m2.moradi@yahoo.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Mehdi Moradi <m2.moradi@yahoo.com>
Description: Simulating simple sequential inhibition point patterns on linear networks, Inhomogeneous linear empty space function, Inhomogeneous linear nearest neighbour function, Inhomogeneous linear J-function, Simulating envelopes for inhomogeneous higher-order summary statistics, Border extraction of linear networks.
